title: You can always Go, "DOWNTOWN" ...to this 2br corner apt!
posting_body: ['Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a Guided Tour Today!', 'As Petula Clark sings..."when you\'re alone and life is making you lonely" you can always go, downtown!', 'So, come on down to this 2br 2 bath MAPLE floorplan!', '  Think about this: You come home from a long days work, place your keys on your entry way table and retreat to your side of the apartment.', 'With a shared main living and dining area this apartment is perfect for entertaining the whole team, and you also are able to get away when working from home gets the best of you!', 'With all day natural lighting, being located in the beautiful Lowertown neighborhood, this apartment is screaming to have you call it home.', 'Get a work out in using our 24/7 private Fitness Center and Studio, relax in our indoor heated pool and get toasty warm in our sauna.', 'Mears Park Place is owned and managed by Bigos Management.', 'Conveniently located in trendy Lowertown across from Mears Park, you can walk the skyway down to the river and bike along the Bike trails through the city parks.', 'We are just 2 blocks from Union Depot and the light rail station, which can take you through St. Paul and connects to Minneapolis and the University campus, as well as the airport.', 'Mears Park Place Apartments features:', '* Indoor Pool', '* Sun Patio', '*', 'Rec Room', '* Sauna', '* Tanning Bed', '* Party Room', '* 24hr gym with fitness studio', '* Underground Parking', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule your self-guided tour today!', 'Please reference apartment #728!', '*Pricing and availability are both determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.']
